flowRoot.flowPara: w - Jump by start of words
e - Jump to end of words
G - Go to end of file
gg - Go to start of file
J - Join line below to the current one
C - Change to the end of line
cw - Change to the end of word
cb - Change to the begining of word
s - Delete character and substitute text
:set ignorecase/noignorecase - Set vim case sensitive or not case sensitive
:set hlsearch/nohlsearch - Activate/Deactivate highlight of searching matches
I - Insert at beginning of the line
A - Append at the end of line
ea - Append at end of word
o - Move to other end of marked area
O - Move to other corner of block
zf - Fold marked text (on visual mode)
:sh - Spawn shell (back to vim with Ctrl+D)
{y,d}G - {Yank,Delete} to the end of the file
{y,d}gg - {Yank,Delete} to the begining of the file
* - Search for word under the cursor
# - Search backward for word under the cursor
n - Repeat search in same direction (next)
N - Repeat search in opposite direction
:%s/old/new/gc - Repleace all "old" with "new" throughout file with confirmations
:e filename - Edit a file in a new buffer
:sp filename - Open a file on split window
:vsp filename - Open a file on vertical split
